David Mendenhall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Mendenhall 0 David Mendenhall (born June 13, 1971) is an American film, television and voice actor. He is perhaps best known for his roles in the films Space Raiders, Over the Top, The Transformers: The Movie and They Still Call Me Bruce.
